criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  African American (AA) female and sexually active with a male partner(s) within the
             past 6 months;

          -  Age 15-24 years;

          -  Initiating contraception;

          -  English speaking

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Not currently pregnant or intending pregnancy within the next 6 months

          -  Not currently using the implant or intrauterine device (IUD).
